John Boxer (British actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Boxer_(British_actor) 0 John Boxer (25 April 1909 – 22 August 1982) was a British film and television actor.Boxer's television appearances included Emergency – Ward 10, Dixon of Dock Green, The Saint, Randall and Hopkirk (Deceased), The Onedin Line and The Life and Times of David Lloyd George.
